	(text "ESP32-S3-DevKitC-1 header. Pin map per CLAUDE.md: GPIO4/5=E22 UART,\nGPIO6/7/8=E22 AUX/M0/M1, GPIO9=config button, GPIO2=LED,\nGPIO11/12=OLED I2C (RX only), GPIO16/17=Pixhawk TELEM2 (TX only).\nAll other header pins explicitly no-connect (deliberately unused)." (at 12.7 15.24 0) (effects (font (size 1.5 1.5))) (uuid "4f039198-44ac-4daf-8ee3-b569ef7a8391"))
